window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Forged in fire.</b></p> <p>Miraculously, Alex had survived the crucible of combat and emerged victorious, earning the right to attend Dragon Academy.</p> <p><b>But his trials had only begun.</b></p> <p>For Alex had dared the unthinkable.</p> <p>A despised Ruidian entering Dragon Academy was an abomination the school’s elite would stop at nothing to destroy, eager to cripple or kill him if they possibly could.</p> <p>Even worse, Alex’s mentor was notorious for throwing his disciples into the thick of any conflict, no matter how unfair the odds.</p> <p>Alex knew only two paths lay before him: to be forged in the fires of his enemies’ hate into a killing blade capable of cutting down all his foes...or to be hammered into slag, never to rise again.</p> <p>Eager for a fast-paced Wuxia/LitRPG adventure filled with deadly adversaries, exotic adventures, and mighty cultivators fighting for the power to topple kingdoms? Then listen on!</p>"; 
